%U A395150 1,8788,2372113,47024926,118535320,47024926,2372113,8788,1,1,33098,29517773,1665033083,10515658661,10515658661,1665033083,29517773,33098,1
%N A395150 Triangle of coefficients of the characteristic polynomial of the negative Pascal matrix with (i+1,j+1)-th entry -C(i+j+1,j).
%C A395150 Row sums seem to be products of consecutive terms in A005158.
%C A395150 Alternating row sums of even index 2n seem to be A005156(n)^2 times A000984(n).
%C A395150 For example, 1 - 49 + 150 - 49 + 1 = 3^2 * 6.
%e A395150 The first few rows are
%e A395150   1;
%e A395150   1, 1;
%e A395150   1, 4, 1;
%e A395150   1, 14, 14, 1;
%e A395150   1, 49, 150, 49, 1;
%e A395150   1, 175, 1574, 1574, 175, 1;
%o A395150 (SageMath)
%o A395150 def m(d):
%o A395150     return matrix(d, d, lambda i, j: -binomial(i + j + 1, j))
%o A395150 [list(m(d).charpoly()) for d in range(10)]
%Y A395150 Similar to A045912 and A395149.
%K A395150 nonn,tabl,new
%O A395150 0,5
%A A395150 _F. Chapoton_, Apr 14 2026
